metadata.name: PAIN INTO POWER
metadata.description:
“Give a woman pain and she'll turn it into power. 
Give that woman chaos and she'll create peace.” 
R.H. Sin

The red dragon signifies passion, strength, and love. The raw power is all her own. 

A 1/1 original illustration by me, Kate Philipson. 

JPEG 3000 x 3000 px
